messages.content: When a new email arrives in Gmail, save the attachment to Google Drive.

{"name": "Email to Drive", "nodes": [{"parameters": {}, "name": "Start", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.start", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [250, 300]}, {"parameters": {"resource": "message", "operation": "watch", "labelIds": ["INBOX"]}, "name": "Gmail Trigger", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.gmail", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [500, 300]}, {"parameters": {"operation": "upload", "binaryData": true, "parentId": "root"}, "name": "Google Drive Upload", "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive", "typeVersion": 1, "position": [750, 300]}], "connections": {"Start": {"main": [[{"node": "Gmail Trigger", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}, "Gmail Trigger": {"main": [[{"node": "Google Drive Upload", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}}, "active": false}
